Under a statement from the artist on one of the gallery walls, Manning calls with her huge signature (the letter &quot;i&quot; in the surname is dotted with heart) after the end of &quot;self-factionalism based on gender, race, sexuality and culture.&quot;
On the opposite side are the sequences of its mitochondrial DNA - the centipede of the letters C, G and A recorded in pencil.
